text: Hey, you know it's Ryan's birthday next week! I wanna get him something.
Ok well, what do you wanna get for him?
I don't know.. what about.. a nice shirt?
A shirt? Well that's fine, but what happens to it after 2 years? It'll be old and out of fashion.
Maybe you should get him a photo frame. That'll be nice, isn't it?
A photo frame? Nah, that's so boring.
Oh, the new iPhone 6s just came out. Should I get him that? Oh, but it's so expensive, I can't afford it.
Ah ah! I know! I'll make him a cake! I remember now, Ryan has a sweet tooth.
